Serializable, org.springframework.web.ErrorResponse
public class EntityNotFoundException extends org.springframework.web.server.ResponseStatusException
Exception thrown when an entity is not found in the database. Returns a 404 NOT FOUND HTTP status with a message indicating the entity type and query used to search for it.
